cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is about image inpainting, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper proposes a GAN-based model that incorporates semantically interpretable information, which involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning and natural language processing. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories. The paper also involves image manipulation, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.GR (Graphics).
